<p>Now, however, as production on TV shows begins to adapt in order to resume, the series has continued filming, and those eagerly awaiting news on whether they have made the finals have been told.</p>

<p>On Sunday, ITV aired the first episode in the series reboot, which saw the judges select their favourite acts to go through.</p>

<p>After bickering about keyboard-playing dinosaurs and terrifying contortion acts, the judges called each of the auditionees and told them who'd made the cut.</p>

